Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是记录媒体的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是旧式的 但应该没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以复原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许其中记录着我们没有见过的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:00:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 可以了！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是说过会带我参观加尔刚蒂亚的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近哥很忙 没这个闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎么这么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都在火海中和我互许终生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 和你这种野蛮泼辣的妹子比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔端庄的小姐更是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 拆除之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 映出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我们的机器还是第一次读出如此详细的数据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是设计图 或者是操纵手册吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人形机器人不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以技术水平来看 这东西和Chamber更为接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗机器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作这东西的人们走向了宇宙 并最终构筑了银河同盟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便离开了冻结的地球 他们仍旧没有放弃斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可悲 但这确实是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须从中吸取教训 避免重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到库盖尔舰团上也有这么棒的店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能消停点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这些料理加尔刚蒂亚上可都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没有点这么多的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会负责吃光的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？啊…是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出远门的时候我都会坐这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛真的很喜欢机械之类的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼欧都想把她挖走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候是情不自禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还去看了Chamber的驾驶舱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…也是情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还开着潜水人形机器人去救雷德了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…别再说这个话题了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是大家太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的菜过会儿呈上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还打算吃那么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法跑来跑去和长时间运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我天生心脏就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也没法治疗 所以我只能去适应它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有姐姐陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有医生 雷德和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真坚强呢 贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你也很坚强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 你在一个陌生的地方开始了生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却像这样交到了朋友 工作着 活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很弱小 但却都很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 莉玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说要先回一趟自己的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是想要洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟今天天气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也回去洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧抓捕对象 把他带走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了 我们的目的是让雷德协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔到底有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能否驾驭这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不弄清楚 就无法将它用于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的知识对我们而言是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用强只会适得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已在捕获Striker驾驶员的行动中失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本国应该已经很不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的死亡是计划之外的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下 应该认为新对象的出现是一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得想办法让雷德自己离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的方针不变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果本国翻脸就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不单单是我们 就连这机体也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你报告一下目前的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民们似乎相当劳累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为接收的前库盖尔舰团人员安排居住地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和维修船只的工作还在继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物资不足这点也很让人担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天虽然从商船那里补充了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为人员增加 所以消费也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光只是时间问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零件和电池都搞不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各个公会都很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长 希望你能采取一些对策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地方 短缺的用品应该都可以得到补充
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说休闲设施也都很完善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是舰团长莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事需要向大家宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始 加尔刚蒂亚将前往海上货易据点 通称龙宫城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 龙宫城是什么地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各船主们及各公会制定好物资采购计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 我们也充分考虑了居民的慰劳问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龙宫城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大规模的设施竟然能漂浮在海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 好多海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂 纱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是第一次这么近距离看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 玩个痛快吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔没办法来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么大的地方逛来逛去 对他的身体负担太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他说去帮奥尔德姆医生调查东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他买点礼物回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢各位提交计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会据此来进行贸易谈判的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从同行那里听说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里铁之类的物资好像全都涨价了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜种子和谷物好像也都被买断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 我们出售的东西也可以卖个好价钱喽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是行情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就乘机赚上一笔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为什么是这个时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和陆地的动向有关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和陆地有关？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详情还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以确定的是有部分物资流向了陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要时刻关注陆地各国的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他们接下来会有新的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和龙宫城高层见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会旁敲侧击一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 陆地吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办 头领
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然对这游乐园没啥兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但调查一下也没什么坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像祭典一样呢 莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 要试试看那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个去打想要的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个 像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑一个喜欢的打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意没装子弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海豚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 有好多的海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋哺乳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经离开海洋 后来又回到海中生活的物种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要选择这样的进化之路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到海中的它们 现在到底在追求什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像可以和海豚一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和海豚…一起玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳装都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳装是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啦 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米也准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿内衣不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件很适合莉玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 不错 不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 这件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面也有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人羡慕嫉妒恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得艾米他们真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这么开心的事我从来都没有经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你在那个库盖尔舰团嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么心事就和我们说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是同伴也是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想 要是能像那样和哥哥一起玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原来有哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舰团上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得帅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所需要的物资 我们应该都能够提供
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大舰团加尔刚蒂亚能停泊敝城 我们也是与有荣焉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们出售的商品也十分丰富 可以说是一次互惠互利的贸易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分物资的流动存在偏向的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只是我杞人忧天 这下心里就踏实了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的消息还真是灵通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们而言 每一位客户都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不会厚此薄彼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最新的世界地图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面也标记了各势力的分布情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我们表示友好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知几位之后是否方便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必接受我们的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着就像能做出各种各样的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就选这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 你们都在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见啊 你们会来这种店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品味不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在给贝贝尔买礼物 正打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子们就老老实实地回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是大人的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的时间算什么玩意儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢败坏风气 我可不会轻饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了防止居民给龙宫城添麻烦 我正在看守！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊…喝多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让她喝的啊！这样子简直太糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我们要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就两个大老粗去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你说的 当然是现找一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 可以还给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚夺走的我的那颗心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这样儿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 莉玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本国那边已经开始做回收准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在部队到达之前没有达成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动就会被终止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 他们打算把马兹尔也舍弃掉吗？这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高机密的兵器不能再这样放置于国外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面应该是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们最害怕的就是情报被泄露给敌国了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我想办法压下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一会儿就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械自行解析并运用语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是遗失的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会说话的机器…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Chamber那样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是像它那样的人工智能的前身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连这种东西都造出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不更深入地和人类交流 就无法度过严酷的冰河期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人形机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那个设计图里的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 我希望你能来我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助我研究这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.94,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,检测到了生命体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔 我可能会让你置身险境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.67,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像记录中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 还是不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:05.74,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像记录中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我无法理解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我开动了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有这一条路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我却开始讨厌战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了？要单独和我谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:22:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能帮我说服雷德 让他离开加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我不懂 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然还有艾米和贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望雷德 艾米和贝贝尔跟我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去哪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？莉玛你是陆地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾米来的话 雷德肯定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.60,0:23:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是觉得不能丢下你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能离开加尔刚蒂亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地上也许有办法治好贝贝尔的病
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次见到陆地上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告诉过我 不要和陆地人有所瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到莉玛是陆地人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使她说让我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是移居到陌生的地方这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.39,0:24:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果能治好贝贝尔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.28,0:24:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果治不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让那孩子陷入危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.94,0:24:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.97,0:24:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.95,0:25:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.26,0:25:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4点钟方向有舰团正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.58,0:25:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.06,0:25:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有见过的船影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.78,0:25:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海贼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.70,0:25:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.38,0:26:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让护卫舰出动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.47,0:26:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究还是打算来硬的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.56,0:26:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不通知我们一声就现身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.01,0:26:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明已经把我们连同行动一起放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.89,0:26:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要抓到雷德 就是我们说的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.94,0:26:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃掉莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.13,0:26:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.92,0:26:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告接近中的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.59,0:26:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是加尔刚蒂亚舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.61,0:26:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告知贵舰团的所属以及行动目的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长 那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.22,0:26:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像不是海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.34,0:27:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚开始就一直以现在的距离和我们并行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.42,0:27:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.30,0:27:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的警戒对象都没有装备连接器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗用的船只…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝罗兹 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.76,0:27:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.01,0:27:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 你知道什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.41,0:27:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接近的舰团到底是什么来历？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.25,0:27:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从陆地而来的特务舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.02,0:27:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.96,0:27:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.36,0:27:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前说过 陆地上也许能治好贝贝尔的病
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.75,0:27:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也会被迫过上比疾病更痛苦的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.87,0:27:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隐瞒了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.10,0:27:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是卡奇纳斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.14,0:27:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.34,0:27:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.83,0:27:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.50,0:27:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.36,0:27:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.68,0:27:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被突然出现的两个男人抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.50,0:27:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自作主张！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.48,0:27:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.81,0:27:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在之前去过的那家食堂附近
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.49,0:28:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.43,0:28:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.39,0:28:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.22,0:28:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目标是你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.48,0:28:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.62,0:28:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.81,0:28:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你被抓的话就无法回到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.89,0:28:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去说服他们把艾米带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.22,0:28:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄刻阿诺斯号 紧急联络！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.05,ruby,NTP,0,300,0,,Oceanus
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.05,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：希腊神话中大洋河的河神
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.71,0:28:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.10,0:28:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个有精神的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.62,0:28:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻释放人质！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.62,0:28:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.15,0:28:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在可是我们的生命线
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.91,0:28:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以这女孩的生命为筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.27,0:29:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对象就会帮忙帮到底的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.15,0:29:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.57,0:29:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然特务舰队已经现身
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.75,0:29:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明一切都迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.59,0:29:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划已经被放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.05,0:29:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么就是不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.25,0:29:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.58,0:29:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只管完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.58,0:29:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.33,0:29:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.85,0:29:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.37,0:29:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西果然不是人形机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.38,0:29:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 这到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们称它为强化外装
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:54.21,ruby,NTP,250,0,0,,Augmented body
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.82,0:29:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫马兹尔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.60,0:29:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的同伴在驾驶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.06,0:29:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.75,0:30:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是同伴 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.15,0:30:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮击？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.90,0:30:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面来电
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰队的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.21,0:30:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是歼灭正在脱离贵舰团的船舶 人员以及装备
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该船舶属于我国
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.06,0:30:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望贵舰团不要进行妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.10,0:30:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法认可
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.77,0:30:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两船上都确认到了本舰团的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请终止攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我国的正当权利 贵舰团已处在我军的舰炮射程内
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.77,0:30:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵舰团的阻挠行为 我们将以武力加以排除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.63,0:30:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.02,0:30:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 不能放任居民的安全受到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.11,0:31:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰做好攻击准备 强化警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.15,0:31:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰请开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.11,0:31:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 乘上来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了艾米 我无论如何都必须保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.13,0:31:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.37,0:31:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.33,0:31:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想把你卷进陆地上已经历时几百年的国与国的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.59,0:31:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获取胜利 我曾想利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在我已经做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有权利破坏你们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.97,0:31:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.46,0:31:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乘上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.34,0:32:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非战斗人员请撤到舰团左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.66,0:32:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 非战斗人员请撤到舰团左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.26,0:32:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别推我！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.60,0:32:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别推！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.76,0:32:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人不在我们的射程内
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.50,0:32:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边推进边警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.02,0:32:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到敌人大型舰开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各护卫舰 做好迎击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.16,0:32:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认两侧交差着弹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.51,0:32:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离已经被对方测量到了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.06,0:32:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.91,0:32:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰允许应战
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.52,0:33:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.78,0:33:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去避难！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.60,0:33:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.11,0:33:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.12,0:33:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.12,0:33:34.38,ruby,NTP,0,180,0,,Adios
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.94,0:33:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.56,0:33:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头领
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.00,0:33:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集情报辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.85,0:33:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜此所赐 我下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.42,0:34:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.91,0:34:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.08,0:34:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没见过这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西正在扩张控制系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.15,0:34:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.74,0:34:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.19,0:34:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从来没发生过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.06,0:34:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能开得动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.55,0:34:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.98,0:34:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像它的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.32,0:34:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.07,0:34:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在脑海里描绘出你想做的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.98,0:34:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你想让这家伙做的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.52,0:34:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这东西的机制和Chamber一样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.45,0:34:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它应该能领会的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.95,0:35:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到那个地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.03,0:36:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.57,0:36:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保镖工作关门大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去做海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.23,0:36:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在不想和陆地那边扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.26,0:36:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 唯有这次不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.99,0:36:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹个痛快 就当是离舰声明了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.43,0:36:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.06,0:36:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别停歇！继续开炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.43,0:36:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电磁兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.74,0:37:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.70,0:37:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.17,0:37:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.39,0:37:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.60,0:37:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.43,0:37:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.28,0:37:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.45,0:37:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.51,0:37:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.27,0:37:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲着我来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.28,0:37:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着机体还没有流入他国 就先沉在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.93,0:37:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.03,0:37:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.47,0:37:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶紧离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.03,0:38:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.76,0:38:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在驾驶那东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.70,0:38:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.21,0:38:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没办法像雷德那么顺手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.40,0:38:22.94,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到操作机能显著下降 请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.73,0:38:31.81,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.57,0:38:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗？还是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.73,0:38:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.60,0:39:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.36,0:39:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是部了不起的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.60,0:39:54.41,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认搭乘者的生体情报以及机体的损坏状况
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.15,0:39:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果很多部像你这样的机械都能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.63,0:40:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切就都会乱套
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.99,0:40:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说是战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连生存之地都会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.67,0:40:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 我应该早点让你回归海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.90,0:40:15.84,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,将搭乘者认定为专属驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.31,0:40:23.15,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,将机能维持更新为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.71,0:40:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.21,0:41:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.65,0:41:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔…Sys…tem
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.34,0:41:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是操作界面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.50,0:41:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.60,0:42:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是马兹尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.37,0:42:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.97,0:42:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.10,0:42:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.56,0:42:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.65,0:42:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.58,0:42:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.56,0:42:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！你要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.17,0:42:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.04,0:42:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.66,0:42:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.27,0:43:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.87,0:43:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.69,0:43:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.88,0:43:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.68,0:43:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 太好了 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.08,0:43:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那里别动 我现在就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.17,0:43:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已经不能回到加尔刚蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.85,0:43:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.77,0:43:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变成这样 都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.94,0:43:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个过错是不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.91,0:43:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟这些没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.11,0:43:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就别管这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.36,0:44:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言 马兹尔就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.78,0:44:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.98,0:44:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.37,0:44:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.90,0:44:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得得救了 你却不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.50,0:44:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇 快带莉玛回来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.93,0:44:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要就此告辞 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.84,0:44:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇…诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.68,0:44:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那眼神 就像活着本身就已经是对你的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.09,0:44:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.30,0:44:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.64,0:44:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有接受这份罪行的觉悟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.39,0:45:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.00,0:45:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我用这种方法赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.48,0:45:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.68,0:45:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.39,0:45:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为海洋只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.82,0:45:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.50,0:45:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 长期以来的修复工作真是辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.40,0:46:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 加尔刚蒂亚又增加了一个新的生活据点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.45,0:46:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚我们所遭遇的身份不明的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.64,0:46:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是陆地国家所拥有的海上力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.72,0:46:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏护卫舰的奋斗以及各位的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.58,0:46:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得受害情况缩减到了最低
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.82,0:46:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎来了新的船只之后
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.05,0:46:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加尔刚蒂亚今后也必须是一个和平昌盛的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.90,0:46:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 请各位助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.91,0:46:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架机体确实和这东西连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.98,0:46:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地球上还有我所不知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.72,0:46:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.40,0:46:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛出生在战争连连的陆地上
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.53,0:46:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎样生活下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.21,0:46:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怀着怎样的心情看待我们的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.57,0:47:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.27,0:47:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛告诉过我 她不想破坏我们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.68,0:47:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管遇到怎样的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.88,0:47:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要在这里生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.01,0:47:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在这里保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.50,0:47:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
