Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:41.74,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自然而然的幸福满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:46.42,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们找到了开始的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.95,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}日出日落 冬去春来 世界不断变迁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.97,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们张开心的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:01.80,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}度过一天又一天的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.89,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论面对怎样的风向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.07,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终朝着自由的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:16.05,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:20.41,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为那悲伤的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:25.43,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}存在着绽放的光芒
